Invocation Name: point pleasant
des: after opening Point Pleasant, the user can ask Alexa about the town. They can also say breakfast, coffee, lunch, dinner, or attractions to hear suggestions for different places within the town that fit into one of the categories.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
